{"tid":1844243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解1月29咁重要嘅行動都冇人推!!!!","createTime":"2020-01-26T14:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T13:04:09.000Z","uid":201311,"like":69,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"0011e71004e2a3f890eba71e0d88a7ba028cd984","tid":1844243,"uid":201311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0QfdyF8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0QfdyF8.jpg&h=fceaaedd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個政府仲想害死幾多人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係時候港人自救!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>同我推爆佢</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422daa58321401a21af3d879e2d70f2db49da043","tid":1844243,"uid":201311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38d65cf7ae967b7664ebdda560efc0b2c188804f","tid":1844243,"uid":201311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"564963ff3eb5a7c90e85fb94d69fcf7df395f71a","tid":1844243,"uid":201311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281531c328a2f872c951d2ea74e3c4baeab4967a","tid":1844243,"uid":178108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e494860bc79b88b9fe5af0fbee3434de52d3258a","tid":1844243,"uid":201311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab08ef88371f2cc1fb1993876b3d271e7599c65","tid":1844243,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:24:36.000Z","msg":"【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ABcOV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ABcOV7.jpg&h=0f21f561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑑於中國肺炎疫症嚴峻，港共政府倒行逆施，徹底失去民意信任，已經無力領導現今疫症。<br />\n加上此疫症已經在香港鄰近地區面臨失控下，有機會令香港國家陷入危機，影響香港國家存亡。<br />\n<br />\n為防止中國肺炎在香港大規模爆發，在此宣佈，於香港時間2020年1月26日21時30分正式頒布緊急狀態令<br />\n為免錯過對抗中國肺炎黃金機會，全體連登網民會即時接管香港權力，全力帶領香港國民對抗中國肺炎，以 香港國民福祉為依歸。<br />\n請各位緊記，香港國家一切權力屬於人民，港共政權並非必然行使權力者。<br />\n<br />\n所有重大事件及決策，將會於連登討論區「政事台」討論及表決<br />\n議案帖文將會以【議案】為首以作識別<br />\n<br />\n大多數民意支持，以及正評數量淨值為1000或以上， 該議案會被視作「獲得通過」<br />\n<br />\n正式實現全民參政，全民議政<br />\n議案通過後，將運用全體公民力量及權力，以及民間一切可能的方法實行各種政策 。<br />\n請各位再次緊記，港共政權並非必然行使權力者，權力永遠歸於所有香港國民。<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844124</a>"},{"pid":"59fa3b5ce1accb432192fe61ce639f5e7d69c2d3","tid":1844243,"uid":201311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66827090fc54aba16d8af41ad4597cad262a1ea1","tid":1844243,"uid":201311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b584731b9cc1df9b3b6c49d5893774945a074fb2","tid":1844243,"uid":254210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"